Full living log: `memory/known-pitfalls.md` (read it before debugging tooling issues).

- Windows paths: architecture lint rules normalize backslashes — keep using path-utils helpers.
- Vitest + Nest DI needs the SWC plugin (esbuild drops decorator metadata).
- Shared package must be built before typecheck/tests (`npm run build:shared`).
- exactOptionalPropertyTypes: don't assign `undefined` to optional props; omit the key instead.
- Zod v4: use z.strictObject / z.enum(tuple); avoid deprecated nativeEnum.
